 🌐 AWS Virtual Private Cloud (VPC)
**Amazon Virtual Private Cloud (Amazon VPC)** enables you to create a logically isolated network within AWS where you can securely launch and manage your cloud resources. It gives you complete control over networking, security, routing, and internet access.

