⚖️ Public vs Private Subnet:-
| Feature             | Public Subnet | Private Subnet |
|---------------------|---------------|----------------|
| Internet Access     | ✅ Yes        | ❌ No         |
| Public IP           | ✅ Yes        | ❌ No         |
| Internet Gateway    | ✅ Yes        | ❌ No         |
| NAT Gateway Required| ❌ No         | ✅ Yes        |
| Security            | Medium        | High           |

